<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.6">
<l>kāla cakka rattōṭu veṇcaṅ kaṅkai yēntiṉāy</l>
<l>ñāla muṟṟu muṇṭumiḻnta nārā yaṇaṉē yeṉṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>ōla miṭṭu nāṉaḻaittā loṉṟum vārā yākilum</l>
<l>kōla māmeṉ ceṉṉikkuṉ kamala maṉṉa kuraikaḻalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“You who held up in [your] hand the white conch along with the time discus,</l>
<l>Nārāyaṇa who swallowed [and] spit out the whole world” saying [and] saying so,</l>
<l>even though you do not come at all when I call [you], placing a cry of distress,</l>
<l>your lotus-like tinkling ankleted [feet] are the ornaments for my head.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
